title: ICSI CSEET January 2026 Results Declared
content:
# ICSI CSEET January 2026 Results Declared

Ek important update hai! The Institute of Company Secretaries of India (ICSI) ne Company Secretary Executive Entrance Test (CSEET) ke January 2026 session ke results declare kar diye hain.

Here are the key details:

*   **Result Declaration Date & Time:** The results were declared on January 20, 2026, at 2:00 PM.
*   **Examination Dates:** The CSEET January 2026 examination was conducted on January 10 and January 12, 2026.
*   **Result Format:** Candidates can access and download their Formal e-Result-cum-Marks Statement online. Please note, no physical copy of the Result-cum-Marks Statement will be issued by the Institute.

## Read the Official Document
*   [Download the Official Notification/Circular here](https://www.icsi.edu/home/exam-result/)

*Published on: 21 January 2026*
